{"tid":1022402,"cid":31,"subCid":9,"title":"又係安藤忠雄 北海道 佛陀深埋萬株薰衣草裡！安藤忠雄作品展現莊嚴禪意","createTime":"2019-02-15T03:59:05.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-15T04:11:50.000Z","uid":74778,"like":12,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"304a1c4aa810539610dbd915530543ad37feff8f","tid":1022402,"uid":74778,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-15T03:59:05.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">[佛陀深埋萬株薰衣草裡！安藤忠雄作品展現莊嚴禪意</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/qQkycy8oAlk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FqQkycy8oAlk&d=rje4l1xmTn6y9o%2BHBfPaf4hgI2KbCNwkzH4ce58ZUDE%3D&h=996799e8\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/qQkycy8oAlk</a><br />\n<br />\n每年七月前後，是北海道薰衣草盛開的季節，綻開時薰衣草織成了大片紫色花海，在風中搖曳擺盪，如詩如畫的畫面，營造北海道浪漫的夏日風景。而除了一般花田，在北海道近日也有處相當著名的薰衣草景點，吸引了許多遊客前往造訪，不過說出來可能會有點驚訝，這處景點是北海道知名的墓園「真駒内滝野霊園」。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://www.designwant.com/upload/images/170809-4_01.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.designwant.com%2Fupload%2Fimages%2F170809-4_01.jpg&h=7af21bf2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://www.designwant.com/upload/images/170809-4_02.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.designwant.com%2Fupload%2Fimages%2F170809-4_02.JPG&h=9222991d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://www.designwant.com/upload/images/170809-4_03.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.designwant.com%2Fupload%2Fimages%2F170809-4_03.JPG&h=5e889983&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://www.designwant.com/upload/images/170809-4_04.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.designwant.com%2Fupload%2Fimages%2F170809-4_04.JPG&h=544d909a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://www.designwant.com/upload/images/170809-4_05.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.designwant.com%2Fupload%2Fimages%2F170809-4_05.JPG&h=98e79004&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n真駒内滝野霊園去年適逢 30 周年開園紀念，委請建築大師安藤忠雄為墓園著名的象徵大佛進行建設「頭大佛」（頭大仏）作品，為突顯大佛的莊嚴且營造引人入勝的氛圍，安藤忠雄在高達 13.5 公尺的大佛四周建了種滿薰衣草的山丘將其圍繞，只露出佛頭，在各個季節都展現了祥和的氣質，讓這墓園象徵有了新樣貌。見著了佛頭想要見到佛身，則需穿過山丘中長達 40 公尺的隧道才能來到終點的佛陀圓形大廳，藉由這樣的空間堆疊神秘感，使參拜者見到大佛的期待感更趨濃烈。而到了盡頭，大佛就坐在露天的圓形中庭正中間，參拜者在底下抬頭仰放佛頭，環形的天空將大佛圍繞，框出了佛祖身旁的光，顯得莊嚴無比。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://www.designwant.com/upload/images/170809-4_06.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.designwant.com%2Fupload%2Fimages%2F170809-4_06.jpg&h=703712eb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://www.designwant.com/upload/images/170809-4_07.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.designwant.com%2Fupload%2Fimages%2F170809-4_07.jpg&h=bc9d1275&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://www.designwant.com/upload/images/170809-4_08.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.designwant.com%2Fupload%2Fimages%2F170809-4_08.JPG&h=03e285d5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://www.designwant.com/upload/images/170809-4_09.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.designwant.com%2Fupload%2Fimages%2F170809-4_09.jpg&h=a9170047&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://www.designwant.com/upload/images/170809-4_10.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.designwant.com%2Fupload%2Fimages%2F170809-4_10.jpg&h=a1230f2f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n春夏時節，大佛之丘外層翠綠的草地上會有 15 萬株薰衣草盛開，藍紫色的花毯浪漫地包裹佛像；而來到冬天，北海道下起靄靄白雪，將大佛之丘覆蓋上一層白被，也蓋上了一層靜心寂靜的氛圍。以佛祖為中心，四周隨四季更替繁榮與寂寥，也許更能讓人領悟生命輪迴的道理。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://www.designwant.com/upload/images/170809-4_11.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.designwant.com%2Fupload%2Fimages%2F170809-4_11.jpg&h=6d890fb1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n真駒内滝野霊園<br />\n地址｜札幌市南区滝野 2 番地<br />\n電話｜011 - 592 - 1223<br />\n開放時間｜09 : 00 &ndash; 16 : 00<br />\n <br />\nSource from 真駒内滝野霊園<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.designwant.com/r1789.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.designwant.com%2Fr1789.html&d=rje4l1xmTn6y9o%2BHBfPaf4hgI2KbCNwkzH4ce58ZUDE%3D&h=85245170\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.designwant.com/r1789.html</a>"},{"pid":"349cc3e751d842e2313685000b6c936d7d4f0ada","tid":1022402,"uid":9526,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-15T04:11:50.000Z","msg":"好耐喇喎....."}]}